Use the standard library
This is how to make_palindrome of string:
   Remember that result is string
   Remember that n is string's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      When i is at least (quotient of n and 2), then:
         Add result to item (diff of (diff of n and 2) and i) in string
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is result
Now you know